        "data": "<h1 class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\" id=\"01H8066N1X71BMWR8KPQVMTM4A\">Service Updates for Liferay Cloud</h1>\n\n<p>The services update for 06/05/2025 is a <strong>patch</strong> update for <strong>CI </strong>service.</p>\n\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"1307\"><strong>Warning&nbsp; :</strong></p>\n\n<div class=\"overflow-auto portlet-msg-alert\">A few customers have found issues when updating to this version. If you face issues with services customizations you made, we suggest updating to version 6.1 or above.</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"01H8066N1X678XQSM8P38E9Q5Z\">DXP Cloud Stack&nbsp;</h2>\n\n<table class=\"table table-autofit table-list table-nowrap\" style=\"width: 637px; height: 170px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: auto;\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr style=\"height: 62px;\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 84.8px; height: 62px; background-color: #969996;\"><strong>Service Name</strong></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 68.3px; height: 62px; background-color: #969996;\"><strong>Previous Release</strong></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 61.2833px; height: 62px; background-color: #969996;\"><strong>Current Release</strong></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 377.617px; height: 62px; background-color: #969996;\"><strong>Docker Images</strong></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</thead>\n\t<tbody valign=\"top\">\n\t\t<tr style=\"height: 48px;\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 84.8px; vertical-align: top; height: 10px;\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Backup</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 68.3px; vertical-align: top; height: 10px;\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.23.0</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 61.2833px; vertical-align: top; height: 10px;\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.23.1</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-right\" style=\"width: 377.617px; vertical-align: top; height: 10px;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\">liferaycloud/backup:5.23.1</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 84.8px; vertical-align: top; height: 10px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>CI</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 68.3px; vertical-align: top; height: 10px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>6.0.1</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 61.2833px; vertical-align: top; height: 10px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>6.0.2</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-right\" style=\"width: 377.617px; vertical-align: top; height: 10px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\"><strong>liferaycloud/jenkins:2.479.3-lts-jdk21-6.0.2</strong></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr style=\"height: 41.2222px;\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 84.8px; vertical-align: top; height: 10px;\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Database</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 68.3px; vertical-align: top; height: 10px;\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.6.3</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 61.2833px; vertical-align: top; height: 10px;\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.6.4</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-right\" style=\"width: 377.617px; vertical-align: top; height: 10px;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\">liferaycloud/database:5.6.4</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 84.8px; vertical-align: top; height: 26px;\">Liferay</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 68.3px; vertical-align: top; height: 26px;\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.8.3</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 61.2833px; vertical-align: top; height: 26px;\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.8.4</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-right\" style=\"width: 377.617px; vertical-align: top; height: 26px;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\">liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.4-5.8.4</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\">liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.3-5.8.4</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\">liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.2-5.8.4</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\">liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.1-5.8.4</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 84.8px; vertical-align: top; height: 26px;\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Search</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 68.3px; vertical-align: top; height: 26px;\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.4.0</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 61.2833px; vertical-align: top; height: 26px;\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.4.1</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-right\" style=\"width: 377.617px; vertical-align: top; height: 26px;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\">liferaycloud/elasticsearch:8.17.5-5.4.1</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\">liferaycloud/elasticsearch:7.17.28-5.4.1</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 84.8px; vertical-align: top; height: 26px;\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Webserver</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 68.3px; vertical-align: top; height: 26px;\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">6.2.0</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 61.2833px; vertical-align: top; height: 26px;\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">6.2.1</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-right\" style=\"width: 377.617px; vertical-align: top; height: 26px;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\">liferaycloud/nginx:1.26.3-6.2.1</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"01H8066N1YWTXV16JYNYMDV6F4\">Change Log</h2>\n\n<table class=\"table table-autofit table-list table-nowrap\" style=\"margin-left: 0px; margin-right: auto; height: 117px; width: 651px;\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr style=\"height: 62px;\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 84.7969px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Service Name</strong></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 62.6719px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Service Version</strong></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 103.797px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Ticket No.</strong></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 354.734px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Description</strong></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</thead>\n\t<tbody valign=\"top\">\n\t\t<tr style=\"height: 81px;\">\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 84.7969px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 11px;\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>CI</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 62.6719px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 11px;\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>6.0.2</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 103.797px; vertical-align: top; height: 11px;\">\n\t\t\t<p><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-46118\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">LCD-46118</a></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 354.734px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 11px;\">\n\t\t\t<p>Fix CI plugins incompatibility issues</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h2 id=\"h_01HFQQE47127T9RVN8YK7MKH4R\">Update Instructions</h2>\n\n<p><strong>Note</strong> : To take advantage of the new features and fixes provided by the 5.x stack of services, you must update your entire stack to the new 5.x images or above.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"01H8066N1YDXGGCTPJ2C2XKQWE\">Image Update Instructions</h2>\n\n<p>The Liferay Cloud image versions needs to be set inside of the &lt;service&gt;/LCP.json file.</p>\n\n<p>Note, however, that the liferay service uses two image properties. The DXP Cloud image is set in the liferay/LCP.json file, but the liferay/dxp image is set in the gradle.properties. This change was made in order to facilitate easier deployment using the Liferay Cloud CLI.</p>\n\n<p>liferay/LCP.json file would set the liferaycloud/liferay-dxp image:&nbsp;</p>\n\n<pre>\"image\":\"liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.4-5.X.X\"</pre>\n\n<p>liferay/gradle.properties file would set the liferay/dxp image:</p>\n\n<pre>liferay.workspace.docker.image.liferay=liferay/dxp:2024.q1.1</pre>\n\n<p>For all other images, you will just need to update the LCP.json file with the intended image version.</p>\n\n<p>Once the LCP.json files are updated, commit the changes to your Git repository.</p>\n\n<pre>git add . &amp;&amp; git commit -m \"Update dxp cloud stack to XXX\"</pre>\n\n<p>After pushing these changes to the remote repository, a build will be created in Liferay Cloud and it is ready to deploy.</p>"
